beer.beer_name: Just Another IPA: Mosaic + East Kent Goldings
beer.beer_description:
Introducing THE THIRD release in our newest BEER SERIES….

It's Just Another IPA!
MOSAIC + EST KENT GOLDING: It's unlikely you'll see these two hops very often in a beer and the outcome is a winner! Old English charm with a touch of earthy spice meets the new world onslaught of tropical mosaic!
